    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make the discarding of syringes in a public place a specific criminal offence",
        "additional_details": "Too many towns are littered with used syringes, that pose a risk to the public and especially children.\r\n \r\nMaking discarding these syringes a specific offence would empower the police to tackle this problem, and ensure that perpetrators faced real penalties.\r\n",
        "background": "The Government should create a specific criminal offence of discarding syringes in a public place, with penalties up to and including custodial sentences.",
